## Styling Guide

### Color Scheme

- **User Messages**: `bg-blue-500` (primary blue)
- **AI Messages**: `bg-gray-100` (light gray) / `dark:bg-gray-800`
- **AI Avatar**: `from-purple-500 to-pink-500` (gradient)
- **System Messages**: `bg-gray-100` (normal) / `bg-red-100` (error)
